OL,3,CMan injured in sword attack thanks
OL,4,Cemergency services for saving his life
OL,6,FA man injured in the sword attack in
OL,7,Feast London has thanked the emergency
OL,8,Fservices and his family for saving his
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FHenry De Los Rios Polania, 35, an IT
OL,12,Fengineer from Hainault, is currently
OL,13,Fin hospital after being stabbed in his
OL,14,Fhome on Tuesday morning.
OL,16,FMr De Los Rios Polania was described
OL,17,Fby his sister, Jessica De Los Rios,
OL,18,F31, as a "hero" for protecting his
OL,19,Ffamily from the assailant.
