OL,3,CMan injured in sword attack thanks
OL,4,Cemergency services for saving his life
OL,6,FHe has since shared a photo to social
OL,7,Fmedia from his hospital bed, with a
OL,8,Fmessage thanking those who saved his
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,F"I would like to start by thanking all
OL,12,Fthe nurses, paramedics, and the
OL,13,Fdoctors on the NHS for keeping me
OL,14,Falive," he said in a post to Instagram
OL,15,FStories, also sending gratitude to the
OL,16,Fpolice "for risking their lives".
OL,18,FHe also thanked "friends and family"
OL,19,Fand all those who made sure he did not
OL,20,F"bleed out".
