OL,3,CMan injured in sword attack thanks
OL,4,Cemergency services for saving his life
OL,6,FMr De Los Rios Polania added: "I'm
OL,7,Frecovering. I have a long journey
OL,8,Fahead but I'm very positive that this
OL,9,Ftrauma will end soon."
OL,11,FHis sister previously said her brother
OL,12,Fwas recovering in hospital after
OL,13,Fsustaining a deep wound to his hand.
OL,15,F"It's a very long process to get his
OL,16,Fhand recovered, due to this wound,"
OL,17,Fshe said, adding: "He's awake, he's in
OL,18,Fhospital," but "he lost a lot of
OL,19,Fblood" and "it's going to be a really
OL,20,Flong, traumatising recovery for him."
