OL,3,CMan injured in sword attack thanks
OL,4,Cemergency services for saving his life
OL,6,F"He's very devastated to believe
OL,7,Fsomething like this could happen," she
OL,8,Fsaid, adding: "To us, he's our hero.
OL,9,FHe protected them ` my niece and my
OL,10,Fsister-in-law.
OL,12,F"They were just literally sleeping,
OL,13,Fopened their eyes to see a man with a
OL,14,Fbig machete sword.
OL,16,F"He felt helpless in the moment but to
OL,17,Fus he is our hero. It could have been
OL,18,Fextremely worse."
